## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
## files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons.
##
## Leave this file as-is on project root.

## User-specific files
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebugPublic/
